STMicroelectronics NV, International Business Machine Corporation And Shaspa Advance Smarter Home Initiative
Tuesday, 8 Jan 2013 09:00am EST
STMicroelectronics NV, International Business Machine Corporation and Shaspa announced a collaboration to tap cloud and mobile computing for manufacturers and service providers to provide ways for consumers to manage and interact with their homes’ functions and entertainment systems using multiple user interfaces such as voice recognition and physical gestures for a smarter home. 
